Use the standard library
This is how to unique_digits of x:
   Remember that result is []
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this x's length times:
      Remember that n is item i in x
      Remember that s is tostring of n
      Remember that u is unique_chars of s
      When u's length is s's length, then:
         Add result to n
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   Remember that result is bubble_sort of result
   The answer is result
